# gemma4-31b-agent — general chat + agentic tool-use (non-CN alternate to qwen3-32b-agent)
# Base model: gemma4:31b  (Google, 31.3B, Q4_K_M; capabilities: completion, vision, tools, thinking)
# Customisations: num_ctx raised (Ollama default 2048) -> 131072; sampling retuned for more
#   deterministic agent/tool runs (temperature lowered from gemma4's published default of 1);
#   base template, tools, and vision preserved.
#
#   NOTE: unlike the qwen3-*-agent variants, thinking is NOT disabled here. gemma4 exposes a
#   `thinking` capability and there is no clean PARAMETER to turn it off; forcing it off would
#   mean hand-editing gemma4's chat template, which risks breaking its native tool-calling.
#   Disable per-request instead with "think": false on /api/chat (Open WebUI: Advanced Params).
#
#   Why the context raise matters: Pi talks to Ollama's OpenAI-compatible /v1 endpoint, which
#   cannot pass num_ctx per request — so without this the model is pinned to the 2048 default.
#   Open WebUI uses native /api/chat and can override num_ctx in the UI, but baking it in gives
#   a single durable default across Pi + WebUI + Goose. Raised again 65536 -> 131072 to match the
#   other *-agent models' standard context; fits the 48 GB M4 Pro alongside the 40GB GPU wired
#   memory ceiling.
#
# To recreate on a fresh Ollama install:
#   ollama pull gemma4:31b
#   ollama create gemma4-31b-agent:latest -f gemma4-31b-agent.Modelfile
#
# Mac Mini blob SHA (current): sha256-280af6832eca23cb322c4dcc65edfea98a21b8f8ab07dc7553bd6f7e6e7a3313
#
# To update a single parameter without a full recreate (e.g. num_ctx):
#   curl -s -X POST http://michaels-mac-mini.cosmach.net:11434/api/create \
#     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#     -d '{"model":"gemma4-31b-agent:latest","from":"gemma4-31b-agent:latest","parameters":{"num_ctx":131072}}'

FROM gemma4:31b

PARAMETER num_ctx 131072

# Sampling retuned away from gemma4's published defaults (temperature 1, top_p 0.95) for more
# deterministic agent/tool-call behavior.
PARAMETER temperature 0.2
PARAMETER top_k 64
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
